"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F15896981\">",
"      What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F15896982\">",
